text:
Alex is still one of the most underrated players in the league; however, calling him underrated is still not bad form, unlike similar cases with Derrick White or, say, Jrue Holliday two years ago.  Over a sample of 41+ games played, 7+ DFGA (defensive field goal attempts) per game Alex has:
-DFG% - 45.3% (32nd among guards/swingmen);
-17th among guards/swingmen in defensive matchup difficulty with an average opponent's FG% of 47.3%;
-DIFF% (the difference between a player's DFG% and the average FG% of his matchups) - -2% (23rd place in the same category).
